      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m so excited to share this absolute gem with you! If you\u2019ve been looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, you\u2019ve found it. This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it shows! It\u2019s super clean, runs like a dream, and is just waiting for someone who will love it as much as I have. I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you might have. Let's get you behind the wheel of this beauty!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
