      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46), an uncompromising example of atmospheric engineering. This S54-powered coupe features a 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, delivering a linear 8,000 RPM powerband through a precision 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This chassis has been fastidiously maintained with documented rear subframe reinforcement, a comprehensive Double VANOS overhaul, and preventative rod bearing replacement. The factory M-Variable Differential Lock provides optimal torque distribution, while the suspension geometry remains true to OEM specifications with refreshed bushings for peak lateral rigidity. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a mechanically harmonized icon in its most desirable configuration.",
      "price": 48500.0,
